'''Alain Turnier''' (died 1991) was a [[Haiti]]an historian. He is the author of several best-selling books:

* ''Les Etats-Unis et le Marché Haïtien''
* ''Avec Mérisier Jeannis''
* ''Quand la Nation Demande des Comptes''

